[SPEAKER_00] idu oblaci,

409
00:20:42,539 --> 00:20:43,200
[SPEAKER_00] dima iz nje,

410
00:20:43,200 --> 00:20:45,680
[SPEAKER_00] valja se,

411
00:20:45,680 --> 00:20:48,720
[SPEAKER_00] onaj moj,

412
00:20:48,720 --> 00:20:51,299
[SPEAKER_00] onaj moj.

413
00:20:51,299 --> 00:20:54,200
[SPEAKER_00] Nema ni imena,

414
00:20:54,200 --> 00:20:55,140
[SPEAKER_00] nego moj.

415
00:20:55,140 --> 00:20:59,859
[SPEAKER_00] Moj će ti čovjek to napraviti,

416
00:20:59,859 --> 00:21:01,099
[SPEAKER_00] a ne pita njega hoćeš li.

417
00:21:03,599 --> 00:21:04,599
[SPEAKER_00] ima ga.

418
00:21:04,599 --> 00:21:07,660
[SPEAKER_00] Zato izgleda ko avet.

419
00:21:07,660 --> 00:21:11,059
[SPEAKER_00] Našao, djavao,

420
00:21:11,059 --> 00:21:12,220
[SPEAKER_00] krasan stan.

421
00:21:12,220 --> 00:21:15,259
[SPEAKER_00] Trostruko veća.

422
00:21:15,259 --> 00:21:17,519
[SPEAKER_00] Moje meso.

423
00:21:21,940 --> 00:21:24,059
[SPEAKER_00] i onda povuče pa pljune.

424
00:21:24,059 --> 00:21:28,839
[SPEAKER_00] Nek se zna da je ljudsko biće.

425
00:21:28,839 --> 00:21:33,839
[SPEAKER_00] Majka čovječanstva,

426
00:21:33,839 --> 00:21:35,019
[SPEAKER_00] što od sebe napravi.

427
00:21:35,019 --> 00:21:37,980
[SPEAKER_00] Majka čovječanstva,

428
00:21:37,980 --> 00:21:39,819
[SPEAKER_00] najuzvišenije biće

429
00:21:39,819 --> 00:21:41,680
[SPEAKER_00] u Božjem stvaranju.

430
00:21:41,680 --> 00:21:45,180
[SPEAKER_00] Kad je sve završio,

431
00:21:46,740 --> 00:21:47,640
[SPEAKER_00] kao šlag

432
00:21:47,640 --> 00:21:48,839
[SPEAKER_00] na tortu

433
00:21:48,839 --> 00:21:50,279
[SPEAKER_00] Bog stavlja ženu.

434
00:21:50,279 --> 00:21:55,220
[SPEAKER_00] S najuzvišenijim poslanjem

435
00:21:55,220 --> 00:21:56,480
[SPEAKER_00] da bude majka

436
00:21:56,480 --> 00:21:57,799
[SPEAKER_00] čitavoga njegovoga

437
00:21:57,799 --> 00:21:59,619
[SPEAKER_00] svetog čovječanstva.

438
00:21:59,619 --> 00:22:03,640
[SPEAKER_00] Uzmite litanije

439
00:22:03,640 --> 00:22:04,740
[SPEAKER_00] svetog Josipa.

440
00:22:04,740 --> 00:22:09,160
[SPEAKER_00] I litanije gospine,

441
00:22:09,160 --> 00:22:10,339
[SPEAKER_00] pa usporedite malo.

442
00:22:10,339 --> 00:22:12,119
[SPEAKER_00] Što je muško,

443
00:22:12,119 --> 00:22:12,799
[SPEAKER_00] a što žensko

444
00:22:12,799 --> 00:22:13,720
[SPEAKER_00] za duha svetog.

445
00:22:15,880 --> 00:22:18,059
[SPEAKER_00] Kraljice neba i zemlje

446
00:22:18,059 --> 00:22:19,279
[SPEAKER_00] moli za nas.

447
00:22:19,279 --> 00:22:22,619
[SPEAKER_00] Čuvaru djevice

448
00:22:22,619 --> 00:22:23,619
[SPEAKER_00] moli za nas.

449
00:22:23,619 --> 00:22:29,220
[SPEAKER_00] Duh sveti tako piše

450
00:22:29,220 --> 00:22:29,980
[SPEAKER_00] u litanijama.

451
00:22:29,980 --> 00:22:32,660
[SPEAKER_00] Koja je razlika

452
00:22:32,660 --> 00:22:34,220
[SPEAKER_00] između kraljice i čuvara?

453
00:22:34,220 --> 00:22:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] I nije joj dosta

454
00:22:37,000 --> 00:22:38,019
[SPEAKER_00] što je čuvarica,

455
00:22:38,019 --> 00:22:40,220
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno kraljica,

456
00:22:40,220 --> 00:22:42,019
[SPEAKER_00] nego mora biti

457
00:22:42,019 --> 00:22:42,799
[SPEAKER_00] nešto više.

458
00:22:45,019 --> 00:22:49,380
[SPEAKER_00] E, sad sam se udala,

459
00:22:49,380 --> 00:22:50,299
[SPEAKER_00] sad imam djecu,

460
00:22:50,299 --> 00:22:51,200
[SPEAKER_00] sad mi ne može

461
00:22:51,200 --> 00:22:51,980
[SPEAKER_00] niko ništa reći.

462
00:22:51,980 --> 00:22:54,900
[SPEAKER_00] Moram išti sad

463
00:22:54,900 --> 00:22:56,200
[SPEAKER_00] biti ravnopravna.

464
00:22:56,200 --> 00:22:57,099
[SPEAKER_00] Ma kako ćeš biti

465
00:22:57,099 --> 00:22:57,799
[SPEAKER_00] ravnopravna?

466
00:22:57,799 --> 00:22:58,980
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ne može

467
00:22:58,980 --> 00:22:59,599
[SPEAKER_00] on biti s tobom

468
00:22:59,599 --> 00:23:00,160
[SPEAKER_00] ravnopravna.

469
00:23:00,160 --> 00:23:00,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ti možeš roditi,

470
00:23:00,960 --> 00:23:01,420
[SPEAKER_00] on ne može.

471
00:23:01,420 --> 00:23:02,299
[SPEAKER_00] Kako će biti s tobom

472
00:23:02,299 --> 00:23:03,200
[SPEAKER_00] ravnopravna?

473
00:23:05,200 --> 00:23:06,700
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, ja ću zapovjedati

474
00:23:06,700 --> 00:23:07,420
[SPEAKER_00] vojskom.

475
00:23:07,420 --> 00:23:09,440
[SPEAKER_00] Pa Bog te je postivio

476
00:23:09,440 --> 00:23:10,380
[SPEAKER_00] da dojiš djecu,

477
00:23:10,380 --> 00:23:11,079
[SPEAKER_00] da hraniš,

478
00:23:11,079 --> 00:23:11,619
[SPEAKER_00] rađaš,

479
00:23:11,619 --> 00:23:12,400
[SPEAKER_00] a ne da ubijaš

480
00:23:12,400 --> 00:23:13,460
[SPEAKER_00] Božiju djecu po svijetu.

481
00:23:13,460 --> 00:23:14,559
[SPEAKER_00] Kako može biti žena

482
00:23:14,559 --> 00:23:16,220
[SPEAKER_00] zapovjednik vojske,

483
00:23:16,220 --> 00:23:17,759
[SPEAKER_00] koja ima

484
00:23:17,759 --> 00:23:18,740
[SPEAKER_00] jedan jedini posao

485
00:23:18,740 --> 00:23:19,519
[SPEAKER_00] da ubija ljude.

486
00:23:22,940 --> 00:23:24,119
[SPEAKER_00] Makne one tamo,

487
00:23:24,119 --> 00:23:26,220
[SPEAKER_00] sad ovdje,

488
00:23:26,220 --> 00:23:27,039
[SPEAKER_00] sad tamo,

489
00:23:27,039 --> 00:23:28,180
[SPEAKER_00] oružje koliko treba,

490
00:23:28,180 --> 00:23:29,680
[SPEAKER_00] glado i narode,

491
00:23:29,680 --> 00:23:31,619
[SPEAKER_00] a vi radite svoj posao.

492
00:23:31,619 --> 00:23:32,680
[SPEAKER_00] I to da majka

493
00:23:32,680 --> 00:23:33,539
[SPEAKER_00] čovješanstva bude.

494
00:23:33,539 --> 00:23:35,440
[SPEAKER_00] Ima i koje to žele.

495
00:23:35,440 --> 00:23:37,720
[SPEAKER_00] Ako ne može tamo,

496
00:23:37,720 --> 00:23:39,319
[SPEAKER_00] a bit će vojskovođa

497
00:23:39,319 --> 00:23:40,039
[SPEAKER_00] u svojoj kući.

498
00:23:40,039 --> 00:23:44,279
[SPEAKER_00] Zgazit će muža prvoga,

499
00:23:44,279 --> 00:23:46,980
[SPEAKER_00] a onda djeci

500
00:23:46,980 --> 00:23:48,119
[SPEAKER_00] pozavrtati vratove.

501
00:23:48,119 --> 00:23:50,619
[SPEAKER_00] I naći svoju

502
00:23:50,619 --> 00:23:52,140
[SPEAKER_00] najbolju prijateljicu,

503
00:23:52,319 --> 00:23:53,259
[SPEAKER_00] jadna ona,

504
00:23:53,259 --> 00:23:56,380
[SPEAKER_00] kakvog ona kretena

505
00:23:56,380 --> 00:23:57,220
[SPEAKER_00] za muža ima,

506
00:23:57,220 --> 00:23:58,839
[SPEAKER_00] a djeca,

507
00:23:58,839 --> 00:24:01,640
[SPEAKER_00] i jedna takva

508
00:24:01,640 --> 00:24:02,680
[SPEAKER_00] iz one trojke

509
00:24:02,680 --> 00:24:04,359
[SPEAKER_00] govori za svoju djecu,

510
00:24:04,359 --> 00:24:06,039
[SPEAKER_00] one moje zvijeri.

511
00:24:06,039 --> 00:24:08,099
[SPEAKER_00] Zvijeri.

512
00:24:08,099 --> 00:24:10,259
[SPEAKER_00] Majka da za djete kaže zvijeri.

513
00:24:10,259 --> 00:24:17,980
[SPEAKER_00] To je svijet u kojem mi živimo.

514
00:24:17,980 --> 00:24:19,460
[SPEAKER_00] To je tragedija

515
00:24:19,460 --> 00:24:21,200
[SPEAKER_00] u koju se čovjek

516
00:24:21,200 --> 00:24:23,039
[SPEAKER_00] ljubljeno Božje biće,

517
00:24:23,039 --> 00:24:24,519
[SPEAKER_00] koje je stvoreno

518
00:24:24,519 --> 00:24:25,740
[SPEAKER_00] da u njemu bude

519
00:24:25,740 --> 00:24:27,240
[SPEAKER_00] Božja ljubav,

520
00:24:27,240 --> 00:24:28,359
[SPEAKER_00] to je zduh sveti,

521
00:24:28,359 --> 00:24:31,279
[SPEAKER_00] i Božja istina,

522
00:24:31,279 --> 00:24:33,579
[SPEAKER_00] to je krist.

523
00:24:33,579 --> 00:24:38,259
[SPEAKER_00] Razlika između

524
00:24:38,259 --> 00:24:39,140
[SPEAKER_00] Božje istine

525
00:24:39,140 --> 00:24:41,140
[SPEAKER_00] i ljudske istine

526
00:24:41,140 --> 00:24:41,920
[SPEAKER_00] u tome što

527
00:24:41,920 --> 00:24:43,220
[SPEAKER_00] Boga reče i bi.

528
00:24:43,220 --> 00:24:50,740
[SPEAKER_00] Kad kažeš

529
00:24:50,740 --> 00:24:52,079
[SPEAKER_00] ovo drvo je jabuka,

530
00:24:52,079 --> 00:24:55,240
[SPEAKER_00] onda to drvo zaista

531
00:24:55,240 --> 00:24:56,119
[SPEAKER_00] jest jabuka

532
00:24:56,119 --> 00:24:57,519
[SPEAKER_00] i zauvijek je jabuka,

533
00:24:57,519 --> 00:24:58,599
[SPEAKER_00] a ovo je more

534
00:24:58,599 --> 00:24:59,799
[SPEAKER_00] i zauvijek je more.

535
00:25:02,119 --> 00:25:02,859
[SPEAKER_00] i kad kažeš

536
00:25:02,859 --> 00:25:03,960
[SPEAKER_00] more je slano,

537
00:25:03,960 --> 00:25:06,079
[SPEAKER_00] onda je more

538
00:25:06,079 --> 00:25:07,539
[SPEAKER_00] zauvijek slano,

539
00:25:07,539 --> 00:25:10,339
[SPEAKER_00] jer Božja istina

540
00:25:10,339 --> 00:25:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] istvara i održava.

541
00:25:17,400 --> 00:25:18,839
[SPEAKER_00] Zato je čovjek stvoren.

542
00:25:18,839 --> 00:25:20,380
[SPEAKER_00] Da u njemu stanuje

543
00:25:20,380 --> 00:25:21,500
[SPEAKER_00] Božja istina,

544
00:25:21,500 --> 00:25:22,579
[SPEAKER_00] to je krist.

545
00:25:22,579 --> 00:25:25,460
[SPEAKER_00] Bog je duh.

546
00:25:25,460 --> 00:25:29,480
[SPEAKER_00] Porod duha je riječ.

547
00:25:29,480 --> 00:25:32,500
[SPEAKER_00] I čovjek je duh.

548
00:25:32,500 --> 00:25:33,619
[SPEAKER_00] On bez nadahnuća

549
00:25:33,619 --> 00:25:34,640
[SPEAKER_00] ne može ništa učiniti.

550
00:25:34,640 --> 00:25:35,539
[SPEAKER_00] Dođeš na večer,

551
00:25:35,539 --> 00:25:36,859
[SPEAKER_00] gladam pred frižider,

552
00:25:36,859 --> 00:25:38,920
[SPEAKER_00] nešto bi još pojevao,

553
00:25:38,920 --> 00:25:39,640
[SPEAKER_00] a ne znam što.

554
00:25:39,640 --> 00:25:42,059
[SPEAKER_00] Otvoriš i gledaš.

555
00:25:42,059 --> 00:25:45,299
[SPEAKER_00] A gladam samo,

556
00:25:45,299 --> 00:25:46,200
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam što bi jeo.

557
00:25:46,680 --> 00:25:47,559
[SPEAKER_00] A onda ti žena kaže,

558
00:25:47,559 --> 00:25:48,799
[SPEAKER_00] a čuj, pa probaj toga sira.

559
00:25:48,799 --> 00:25:50,420
[SPEAKER_00] A vidiš, dobro si se sjetila.

560
00:25:50,420 --> 00:25:51,220
[SPEAKER_00] Može.

561
00:25:51,220 --> 00:25:52,259
[SPEAKER_00] A tu je stajao.

562
00:25:52,259 --> 00:25:54,819
[SPEAKER_00] Nije on imao nadahnuće,

563
00:25:54,819 --> 00:25:56,160
[SPEAKER_00] nego ona dobila nadahnuće.

564
00:25:56,160 --> 00:25:59,420
[SPEAKER_00] Nadahnuće.

565
00:25:59,420 --> 00:26:00,500
[SPEAKER_00] Bez nadahnuća

566
00:26:00,500 --> 00:26:01,460
[SPEAKER_00] ni jesti ne možeš.

567
00:26:01,460 --> 00:26:04,920
[SPEAKER_00] Hajde nek neko

568
00:26:04,920 --> 00:26:05,960
[SPEAKER_00] bez nadahnuća

569
00:26:05,960 --> 00:26:07,339
[SPEAKER_00] napravi sebi kuću.

570
00:26:07,339 --> 00:26:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne može.

571
00:26:08,000 --> 00:26:12,500
[SPEAKER_00] Pa kad je hoćeš napraviti,

572
00:26:12,500 --> 00:26:13,519
[SPEAKER_00] ma radio bi,

573
00:26:13,519 --> 00:26:14,920
[SPEAKER_00] ali ne znam kako ću je napraviti.

574
00:26:14,920 --> 00:26:16,599
[SPEAKER_00] Moram sad nacrtati,

575
00:26:16,599 --> 00:26:17,279
[SPEAKER_00] što mi treba.

576
00:26:17,279 --> 00:26:19,460
[SPEAKER_00] Pa izračunati imam lija novaca

577
00:26:19,460 --> 00:26:20,539
[SPEAKER_00] toliko da to napravim.

578
00:26:20,539 --> 00:26:22,299
[SPEAKER_00] Pa onda napravi neko

579
00:26:22,299 --> 00:26:24,079
[SPEAKER_00] da bude veća od susjeda.

580
00:26:24,079 --> 00:26:25,180
[SPEAKER_00] Znam jednoga u ratu

581
00:26:25,180 --> 00:26:26,559
[SPEAKER_00] koji je tri puta rušio kuću

582
00:26:26,559 --> 00:26:27,980
[SPEAKER_00] da mu je kuća veća od bratove.

583
00:26:27,980 --> 00:26:31,200
[SPEAKER_00] Jer je on bogata brat,

584
00:26:31,200 --> 00:26:32,539
[SPEAKER_00] glupan koji ne zna zaraditi.

585
00:26:32,539 --> 00:26:33,779
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ja se snađem.

586
00:26:33,779 --> 00:26:36,940
[SPEAKER_00] A on ne zna živjeti.

587
00:26:43,599 --> 00:26:46,700
[SPEAKER_00] Znači kao što je riječ Božja

588
00:26:46,700 --> 00:26:48,940
[SPEAKER_00] porod Boga koji je ljubav,

589
00:26:48,940 --> 00:26:52,619
[SPEAKER_00] tako je i riječ ljudska

590
00:26:52,619 --> 00:26:54,940
[SPEAKER_00] porod čovjeka.

591
00:26:54,940 --> 00:26:59,319
[SPEAKER_00] Vi ne znate tko sam ja dok ne progovorim.

592
00:26:59,319 --> 00:27:02,339
[SPEAKER_00] Tako mi ne znamo

593
00:27:02,339 --> 00:27:04,619
[SPEAKER_00] ni tko je Bog dok ne progovori.

594
00:27:06,680 --> 00:27:08,319
[SPEAKER_00] Imate onaj primjer

595
00:27:08,319 --> 00:27:12,400
[SPEAKER_00] gdje apostoli i zabranici gospodinovi

596
00:27:12,400 --> 00:27:14,180
[SPEAKER_00] tri godine žive s njime.

597
00:27:14,180 --> 00:27:17,799
[SPEAKER_00] I apostol Filip kaže

598
00:27:17,799 --> 00:27:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] gospodine pokaži nam oca

599
00:27:20,000 --> 00:27:20,920
[SPEAKER_00] i bit će nam dobro.

600
00:27:20,920 --> 00:27:22,460
[SPEAKER_00] Bit će nam dosta.

601
00:27:22,460 --> 00:27:25,720
[SPEAKER_00] A Jesu kaže

602
00:27:25,720 --> 00:27:28,740
[SPEAKER_00] Filipe, pa zar još ne razumiješ?

603
00:27:28,740 --> 00:27:31,680
[SPEAKER_00] Tko je vidio mene

604
00:27:31,680 --> 00:27:34,960
[SPEAKER_00] vidio je i oca.

605
00:27:34,960 --> 00:27:38,740
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ja sam u ocu i otac u meni.

606
00:27:38,740 --> 00:27:41,400
[SPEAKER_00] Tko je vidio Isusa,

607
00:27:41,400 --> 00:27:43,019
[SPEAKER_00] vidio je ljubav.

608
00:27:43,019 --> 00:27:44,380
[SPEAKER_00] U njemu je ljubav vidljiva.

609
00:27:44,380 --> 00:27:48,359
[SPEAKER_00] A i mi smo stvoreni

610
00:27:48,359 --> 00:27:50,759
[SPEAKER_00] da ne vidljiva ljubav

611
00:27:50,759 --> 00:27:52,200
[SPEAKER_00] u nama bude vidljiva

612
00:27:52,200 --> 00:27:54,339
[SPEAKER_00] i da ne vidljiva Božja istina,

613
00:27:54,339 --> 00:27:54,720
[SPEAKER_00] Krist,

614
00:27:54,720 --> 00:27:57,180
[SPEAKER_00] i u nama bude vidljiva.

615
00:27:58,680 --> 00:27:59,400
[SPEAKER_00] Pa se kaže

616
00:27:59,400 --> 00:28:01,819
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj čovjek je od riječi.

617
00:28:01,819 --> 00:28:05,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo je dobar čovjek.

618
00:28:05,500 --> 00:28:11,319
[SPEAKER_00] Da bi smo mogli biti

619
00:28:11,319 --> 00:28:14,200
[SPEAKER_00] suradnici Božji,

620
00:28:14,200 --> 00:28:16,680
[SPEAKER_00] a to znači prava ljudska bića

621
00:28:16,680 --> 00:28:20,519
[SPEAKER_00] u kojima prebiva Božji duh,

622
00:28:20,519 --> 00:28:23,019
[SPEAKER_00] duh sveti ili ti ljubav

623
00:28:23,019 --> 00:28:25,880
[SPEAKER_00] i Božja istina,

624
00:28:25,880 --> 00:28:27,220
[SPEAKER_00] da nema druge istine

625
00:28:27,220 --> 00:28:28,519
[SPEAKER_00] una Mikoja Đavolska,

