844
00:34:44,599 --> 00:34:45,340
[SPEAKER_00] zaboraviš.

845
00:34:45,340 --> 00:34:46,860
[SPEAKER_00] Čovjek ne zna da srce ima

846
00:34:46,860 --> 00:34:48,699
[SPEAKER_00] danas dok ga ne strefi infarkt.

847
00:34:48,699 --> 00:34:50,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ajme,

848
00:34:50,199 --> 00:34:50,639
[SPEAKER_00] zamisli,

849
00:34:50,639 --> 00:34:51,199
[SPEAKER_00] imam srce.

850
00:34:53,760 --> 00:34:55,039
[SPEAKER_00] Jedan je u mom kraju govorio,

851
00:34:55,039 --> 00:34:55,400
[SPEAKER_00] kaže,

852
00:34:55,400 --> 00:34:56,940
[SPEAKER_00] nemam srca.

853
00:34:56,940 --> 00:34:57,739
[SPEAKER_00] Kako nemaš srca?

854
00:34:57,739 --> 00:34:59,260
[SPEAKER_00] Porekao doktor da nemam srca.

855
00:34:59,260 --> 00:35:00,619
[SPEAKER_00] On iskreno vjerovao,

856
00:35:00,619 --> 00:35:01,500
[SPEAKER_00] jer je doktor rekao

857
00:35:01,500 --> 00:35:02,079
[SPEAKER_00] da nema srca,

858
00:35:02,079 --> 00:35:02,900
[SPEAKER_00] kucao u njemu.

859
00:35:02,900 --> 00:35:05,199
[SPEAKER_00] Znači.

860
00:35:05,199 --> 00:35:08,400
[SPEAKER_00] Tišina

861
00:35:08,400 --> 00:35:11,199
[SPEAKER_00] i mrak su

862
00:35:11,199 --> 00:35:12,880
[SPEAKER_00] sredstva Božja

863
00:35:12,880 --> 00:35:14,420
[SPEAKER_00] gdje ćeš Boga sresti čuti.

864
00:35:14,420 --> 00:35:16,420
[SPEAKER_00] I kad pogledaš

865
00:35:16,420 --> 00:35:17,719
[SPEAKER_00] ko su najveći

866
00:35:17,719 --> 00:35:19,880
[SPEAKER_00] duhovni oci bili,

867
00:35:19,880 --> 00:35:22,139
[SPEAKER_00] najznačajniji Božji ljudi

868
00:35:22,139 --> 00:35:24,139
[SPEAKER_00] na koje je Bog se mogao osloniti

869
00:35:24,139 --> 00:35:25,280
[SPEAKER_00] da po njima nešto učini,

870
00:35:25,280 --> 00:35:27,820
[SPEAKER_00] to su upravo nekakvi takvi ljudi bili.

871
00:35:27,820 --> 00:35:30,739
[SPEAKER_00] Jedan Abraham.

872
00:35:30,739 --> 00:35:34,320
[SPEAKER_00] Kud ovce tudi on?

873
00:35:34,320 --> 00:35:36,619
[SPEAKER_00] I ima ih sve više.

874
00:35:36,619 --> 00:35:41,059
[SPEAKER_00] Željan čovjeka ide onaj njegov

875
00:35:41,059 --> 00:35:42,800
[SPEAKER_00] od brata mu,

876
00:35:42,800 --> 00:35:43,480
[SPEAKER_00] sin s njime,

877
00:35:43,480 --> 00:35:43,880
[SPEAKER_00] Lod.

878
00:35:43,880 --> 00:35:47,739
[SPEAKER_00] Kad se namnožilo tih puno ovaca,

879
00:35:47,739 --> 00:35:48,139
[SPEAKER_00] kaže,

880
00:35:48,139 --> 00:35:50,380
[SPEAKER_00] rođače da nam se ne svađaju

881
00:35:50,380 --> 00:35:52,059
[SPEAKER_00] pastiri,

882
00:35:52,059 --> 00:35:53,840
[SPEAKER_00] bilo bi dobro da se mi raziđemo.

883
00:35:53,840 --> 00:35:56,460
[SPEAKER_00] Evo ti se okreni okolo,

884
00:35:56,460 --> 00:35:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] pa pogledaj kud god ti kreneš,

885
00:35:58,000 --> 00:35:58,920
[SPEAKER_00] ja ću na drugu stranu.

886
00:35:58,920 --> 00:36:01,559
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, Abraham nije izabrao ništa na zemlji.

887
00:36:01,559 --> 00:36:06,079
[SPEAKER_00] A htio se rastati

888
00:36:06,079 --> 00:36:07,840
[SPEAKER_00] od Lota

889
00:36:07,840 --> 00:36:09,440
[SPEAKER_00] da se ljudi ne svađaju.

890
00:36:09,440 --> 00:36:10,840
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, stalo mu je bilo

891
00:36:10,840 --> 00:36:12,300
[SPEAKER_00] do ljubavi Božje među ljudima.

892
00:36:14,300 --> 00:36:15,079
[SPEAKER_00] i Lod

893
00:36:15,079 --> 00:36:17,179
[SPEAKER_00] oženio se

894
00:36:17,179 --> 00:36:19,599
[SPEAKER_00] na kućnom savjetu,

895
00:36:19,599 --> 00:36:21,159
[SPEAKER_00] dogovori se sa ženom kudbi,

896
00:36:21,159 --> 00:36:21,679
[SPEAKER_00] ona kaže,

897
00:36:21,679 --> 00:36:22,260
[SPEAKER_00] pogled dolje,

898
00:36:22,260 --> 00:36:23,579
[SPEAKER_00] kakva ravnica,

899
00:36:23,579 --> 00:36:24,619
[SPEAKER_00] grad,

900
00:36:24,619 --> 00:36:28,300
[SPEAKER_00] ko će hodati za ovcama po ovim brdima,

901
00:36:28,300 --> 00:36:28,980
[SPEAKER_00] idemo dolje,

902
00:36:28,980 --> 00:36:31,079
[SPEAKER_00] izabere Sodomu.

903
00:36:31,079 --> 00:36:34,159
[SPEAKER_00] I ovaj koji nije izabrao ništa,

904
00:36:34,159 --> 00:36:35,420
[SPEAKER_00] dolazi mu Bog,

905
00:36:35,420 --> 00:36:37,099
[SPEAKER_00] dolje povika nekakva.

906
00:36:37,099 --> 00:36:40,360
[SPEAKER_00] Do neba se čuje koliko dolje se griješi

907
00:36:40,360 --> 00:36:41,019
[SPEAKER_00] u tome gradu

908
00:36:41,019 --> 00:36:43,059
[SPEAKER_00] i ne vidjeti što je govoreo na tri anđela.

909
00:36:43,059 --> 00:36:47,619
[SPEAKER_00] I savjetuju se sa tim čovjekom

910
00:36:47,619 --> 00:36:50,019
[SPEAKER_00] koji je čovjek tišine i dobrote.

911
00:36:50,019 --> 00:36:52,699
[SPEAKER_00] A on se zauzima

912
00:36:52,699 --> 00:36:55,519
[SPEAKER_00] za spas grada.

913
00:36:55,519 --> 00:36:57,679
[SPEAKER_00] I što god je tražio

914
00:36:57,679 --> 00:36:59,179
[SPEAKER_00] taj prijatelj tišine

915
00:36:59,179 --> 00:37:00,760
[SPEAKER_00] i razgovora s Bogom u sebi,

916
00:37:00,760 --> 00:37:03,960
[SPEAKER_00] sve je Bog bio spreman učiniti.

917
00:37:03,960 --> 00:37:07,739
[SPEAKER_00] Pa kad je došlo do zadnjih deset,

918
00:37:07,739 --> 00:37:09,179
[SPEAKER_00] nije se usudio više pitati

919
00:37:09,179 --> 00:37:10,559
[SPEAKER_00] jer je toliko Boga je samo čekao

920
00:37:10,559 --> 00:37:11,920
[SPEAKER_00] što hoćeš, sve ću ti dati

921
00:37:11,920 --> 00:37:13,039
[SPEAKER_00] zato što si moj.

922
00:37:13,039 --> 00:37:17,079
[SPEAKER_00] I na zagovor Lota,

923
00:37:17,079 --> 00:37:18,800
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno Abrahama,

924
00:37:18,800 --> 00:37:20,960
[SPEAKER_00] spašen je Lot

925
00:37:20,960 --> 00:37:23,119
[SPEAKER_00] pravedniku,

926
00:37:23,119 --> 00:37:24,679
[SPEAKER_00] ali i njegova obitelj

927
00:37:24,679 --> 00:37:25,739
[SPEAKER_00] koja nije bila sveta.

928
00:37:25,739 --> 00:37:29,300
[SPEAKER_00] I što je Lot izgubio?

929
00:37:29,300 --> 00:37:30,739
[SPEAKER_00] Je bio pravednik,

930
00:37:30,739 --> 00:37:31,519
[SPEAKER_00] bojao se Boga,

931
00:37:31,519 --> 00:37:35,179
[SPEAKER_00] ali je ipak bio čovjek

932
00:37:35,179 --> 00:37:37,239
[SPEAKER_00] što se veli od krvi i mesa

933
00:37:37,239 --> 00:37:39,239
[SPEAKER_00] od ove zemlje,

934
00:37:39,239 --> 00:37:41,260
[SPEAKER_00] ostao je bez svega imanja,

935
00:37:41,260 --> 00:37:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] ostao je bez žene

936
00:37:44,000 --> 00:37:46,099
[SPEAKER_00] koja se pretvorila u kip od stoli,

937
00:37:46,099 --> 00:37:49,360
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno ogorčena je bila na Boga,

938
00:37:49,360 --> 00:37:51,019
[SPEAKER_00] zašto je ubija ljubavnike

939
00:37:51,019 --> 00:37:53,199
[SPEAKER_00] i njezine najbolje prijateljice tamo

940
00:37:53,199 --> 00:37:53,980
[SPEAKER_00] i ne znam koji.

941
00:37:53,980 --> 00:37:56,679
[SPEAKER_00] Ode, cijelo mi društvo ode.

942
00:37:57,179 --> 00:37:58,760
[SPEAKER_00] Tako smo lijepo uštimali život,

943
00:37:58,760 --> 00:38:00,199
[SPEAKER_00] bili smo najbolje prijateljice,

944
00:38:00,199 --> 00:38:01,219
[SPEAKER_00] najbolji prijatelji,

945
00:38:01,219 --> 00:38:02,260
[SPEAKER_00] podajno, stalno,

946
00:38:02,260 --> 00:38:04,239
[SPEAKER_00] ko zna što je sve bilo tu.

947
00:38:04,239 --> 00:38:08,940
[SPEAKER_00] Zato se pretvorila u kip od soli

948
00:38:08,940 --> 00:38:11,920
[SPEAKER_00] i njezino ime nije zapamćeno.

949
00:38:11,920 --> 00:38:14,179
[SPEAKER_00] Jer koga Biblija spomene,

950
00:38:14,179 --> 00:38:16,460
[SPEAKER_00] ta je zapamćen za uvijek.

951
00:38:16,460 --> 00:38:20,099
[SPEAKER_00] U isto su vrijeme živjeli

952
00:38:20,099 --> 00:38:23,300
[SPEAKER_00] Abraham i Sara

953
00:38:23,300 --> 00:38:25,920
[SPEAKER_00] i Lot i njegova žena.

954
00:38:25,920 --> 00:38:26,539
[SPEAKER_00] Zamislite,

955
00:38:26,539 --> 00:38:29,099
[SPEAKER_00] Lotova žena nema imena u Bibliji.

956
00:38:29,099 --> 00:38:32,340
[SPEAKER_00] Jer je žena ovog svijeta.

957
00:38:32,340 --> 00:38:34,280
[SPEAKER_00] I kogod je čovjek samo ovog svijeta,

958
00:38:34,280 --> 00:38:36,139
[SPEAKER_00] njega zaboravguta,

959
00:38:36,139 --> 00:38:38,280
[SPEAKER_00] ako je Boži čovjek,

960
00:38:38,280 --> 00:38:39,679
[SPEAKER_00] pamte ga sva vremena.

961
00:38:39,679 --> 00:38:43,460
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže Isus, blago vama,

962
00:38:43,460 --> 00:38:45,679
[SPEAKER_00] jer su vam imena zapisana na nebesima.

963
00:38:46,460 --> 00:38:48,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ne gore na oblacima,

964
00:38:48,500 --> 00:38:50,059
[SPEAKER_00] jer nisu to ta nebesa,

965
00:38:50,059 --> 00:38:52,340
[SPEAKER_00] kad kažemo na nebu.

966
00:38:52,340 --> 00:38:55,860
[SPEAKER_00] Nego su to unutrašnja nebesa

967
00:38:55,860 --> 00:38:57,460
[SPEAKER_00] koja nadvisuju moju dušu.

968
00:38:57,460 --> 00:39:00,900
[SPEAKER_00] Ono što je sve veće od moje naravi,

969
00:39:00,900 --> 00:39:03,300
[SPEAKER_00] od moga postojanja,

970
00:39:03,300 --> 00:39:04,420
[SPEAKER_00] stvoritelj moji,

971
00:39:04,420 --> 00:39:07,380
[SPEAKER_00] on je na vrhu tih nebesa u meni.

972
00:39:07,380 --> 00:39:09,159
[SPEAKER_00] I do tih nebesa dolaziš

973
00:39:09,159 --> 00:39:11,599
[SPEAKER_00] s krušenom molitvom,

974
00:39:11,599 --> 00:39:14,579
[SPEAKER_00] isključivanjem iz cijeloga svemira.

975
00:39:14,579 --> 00:39:16,480
[SPEAKER_00] Sad sam samo pred tobom, Bože,

976
00:39:16,480 --> 00:39:17,780
[SPEAKER_00] koji si čista ljubav

977
00:39:17,780 --> 00:39:20,619
[SPEAKER_00] i iščekujem tvoju riječ

978
00:39:20,619 --> 00:39:22,360
[SPEAKER_00] da progovoriš mojoj duši.

979
00:39:22,360 --> 00:39:24,920
[SPEAKER_00] I bdiješ i čekaš

980
00:39:24,920 --> 00:39:26,420
[SPEAKER_00] i kad ta riječ dođe,

981
00:39:26,420 --> 00:39:28,460
[SPEAKER_00] ti se preobraziš.

982
00:39:28,460 --> 00:39:29,679
[SPEAKER_00] Jesi na zemlji,

983
00:39:29,679 --> 00:39:32,320
[SPEAKER_00] ali si iznad zemlje,

984
00:39:32,320 --> 00:39:34,360
[SPEAKER_00] kao da je sav svemir u tebi,

985
00:39:34,360 --> 00:39:37,280
[SPEAKER_00] kao da si središnja točka svemira,

986
00:39:37,280 --> 00:39:38,480
[SPEAKER_00] tako se osjećaš.

987
00:39:39,880 --> 00:39:40,940
[SPEAKER_00] Govorim iz iskustva,

988
00:39:40,940 --> 00:39:42,179
[SPEAKER_00] oni su bajke.

989
00:39:42,179 --> 00:39:45,519
[SPEAKER_00] Gledaš sve od ozgo,

990
00:39:45,519 --> 00:39:46,159
[SPEAKER_00] svi sina.

991
00:39:46,159 --> 00:39:48,219
[SPEAKER_00] U snovima ti pokazuju od ozgo.

992
00:39:48,219 --> 00:39:53,539
[SPEAKER_00] Uvijek ti od ozgo nekako pokazuje zemlju.

993
00:39:53,539 --> 00:39:58,260
[SPEAKER_00] Ali si i konkretno sa svime tu.

994
00:39:58,260 --> 00:39:59,639
[SPEAKER_00] Kad god ovdje dođeš,

995
00:39:59,639 --> 00:40:00,539
[SPEAKER_00] koga god vidiš,

996
00:40:00,539 --> 00:40:03,300
[SPEAKER_00] prilaziš mu ko najdražem svome.

997
00:40:04,000 --> 00:40:07,320
[SPEAKER_00] Jer je isti stvoritelj poželio imena i tebe.

998
00:40:07,320 --> 00:40:12,380
[SPEAKER_00] I kogod od nas krene krivim putem,

999
00:40:12,380 --> 00:40:14,900
[SPEAKER_00] riječ Božja, Božja istina,

1000
00:40:14,900 --> 00:40:17,719
[SPEAKER_00] Krist plače nad nama kao nad Jeruzalemom.

1001
00:40:17,719 --> 00:40:19,579
[SPEAKER_00] O kad bi ti znao što te čeka,

1002
00:40:19,579 --> 00:40:22,099
[SPEAKER_00] jer dolazi vrijeme kad će te neprijatelji tvoji

1003
00:40:22,099 --> 00:40:24,380
[SPEAKER_00] okružiti sa svih strana

1004
00:40:24,380 --> 00:40:27,760
[SPEAKER_00] i smrskati i tebe i djecu tvoju u tebi.

1005
00:40:27,760 --> 00:40:31,440
[SPEAKER_00] Zato jer nisi priznao čas kad te Bog pohodi,

1006
00:40:31,559 --> 00:40:34,880
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno kad ti savjest govori nije to dobro.

1007
00:40:34,880 --> 00:40:37,960
[SPEAKER_00] To je Božji glas u nama.

1008
00:40:37,960 --> 00:40:40,500
[SPEAKER_00] Savjest je Božja riječ.

1009
00:40:40,500 --> 00:40:43,239
[SPEAKER_00] I ona nije dio ljudskog tijela,

1010
00:40:43,239 --> 00:40:44,360
[SPEAKER_00] ni ljudske duše.

1011
00:40:44,360 --> 00:40:46,380
[SPEAKER_00] Zato nju ne možeš ubiti.

1012
00:40:46,380 --> 00:40:49,320
[SPEAKER_00] Ali pogledajte danas kolika je borba

1013
00:40:49,320 --> 00:40:50,940
[SPEAKER_00] protiv priziva savjesti.

1014
00:40:50,940 --> 00:40:52,780
[SPEAKER_00] Zamisli, ja sam joj ubio u sebi

1015
00:40:52,780 --> 00:40:54,480
[SPEAKER_00] i ti ćeš sad imati savjest kraj mene.

1016
00:40:54,480 --> 00:40:57,059
[SPEAKER_00] To treba zabraniti.

1017
00:40:57,059 --> 00:40:59,559
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ako imaš savjest,

1018
00:40:59,840 --> 00:41:01,559
[SPEAKER_00] ne možeš krasti, ne možeš bludničiti,

1019
00:41:01,559 --> 00:41:02,739
[SPEAKER_00] ne možeš ubijati,

1020
00:41:02,739 --> 00:41:04,519
[SPEAKER_00] ne možeš mrziti,

1021
00:41:04,519 --> 00:41:07,300
[SPEAKER_00] ne možeš u karijeri napredovati

1022
00:41:07,300 --> 00:41:09,159
[SPEAKER_00] na lopovski način.

1023
00:41:09,159 --> 00:41:14,159
[SPEAKER_00] To je ozbiljan problem u ovome društvu.

1024
00:41:14,159 --> 00:41:15,719
[SPEAKER_00] Ne mislim Hrvatsko,

1025
00:41:15,719 --> 00:41:17,960
[SPEAKER_00] nego uopće u ovoga vremena u svijetu.

1026
00:41:20,960 --> 00:41:24,480
[SPEAKER_00] I zato je važno njegovati tišine

1027
00:41:24,480 --> 00:41:28,300
[SPEAKER_00] i poštivati mrak.

1028
00:41:28,300 --> 00:41:31,780
[SPEAKER_00] Nije bitno koliko ćeš ti spavati.

1029
00:41:31,780 --> 00:41:35,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ali je bitno kad uđeš na spavanje,

1030
00:41:35,960 --> 00:41:37,719
[SPEAKER_00] nema ništa drugo, ne nosiš unutra.

1031
00:41:37,719 --> 00:41:39,539
[SPEAKER_00] U tvoje ruke, oče,

1032
00:41:39,539 --> 00:41:40,519
[SPEAKER_00] predajem duh svoj.

1033
00:41:40,519 --> 00:41:41,579
[SPEAKER_00] Ja tako kažem.

1034
00:41:41,579 --> 00:41:43,900
[SPEAKER_00] Jer je tako Isus rekao.

1035
00:41:43,900 --> 00:41:46,059
[SPEAKER_00] A slijedom toga,

1036
00:41:46,059 --> 00:41:46,920
[SPEAKER_00] u tvoje ruke,

1037
00:41:46,920 --> 00:41:48,860
[SPEAKER_00] Isuse, predajem dušu svoju.

1038
00:41:49,059 --> 00:41:51,820
[SPEAKER_00] Jer je moja duša zarušnica riječi Božje.

1039
00:41:51,820 --> 00:41:53,559
[SPEAKER_00] Duša govori

1040
00:41:53,559 --> 00:41:56,159
[SPEAKER_00] i Bog duši govori,

1041
00:41:56,159 --> 00:41:57,559
[SPEAKER_00] a to što Bog govori,

1042
00:41:57,559 --> 00:41:58,380
[SPEAKER_00] to je riječ njegova,

1043
00:41:58,380 --> 00:41:58,960
[SPEAKER_00] to je Hrist.

1044
00:41:58,960 --> 00:42:01,440
[SPEAKER_00] Koja tijelom postaje

1045
00:42:01,440 --> 00:42:03,500
[SPEAKER_00] kad ja predam svoje tijelo

1046
00:42:03,500 --> 00:42:05,539
[SPEAKER_00] da riječ Božja u meni živi.

1047
00:42:05,539 --> 00:42:07,519
[SPEAKER_00] Da ne govorim i ne mislim ništa drugo

1048
00:42:07,519 --> 00:42:08,820
[SPEAKER_00] nego što Bog zapovjeda.

