1428
00:53:06,019 --> 00:53:06,880
[SPEAKER_00] I jedan put kaže,

1429
00:53:06,880 --> 00:53:08,440
[SPEAKER_00] molio sam tako za ženu,

1430
00:53:08,440 --> 00:53:10,159
[SPEAKER_00] iskočio mi tlak 220.

1431
00:53:10,159 --> 00:53:12,179
[SPEAKER_00] Odem doktoru,

1432
