[SPEAKER_00] ovoga,

1467
00:54:16,199 --> 00:54:17,639
[SPEAKER_00] negdje početkom vrata,

1468
00:54:17,639 --> 00:54:18,679
[SPEAKER_00] čistio sam garažu,

1469
00:54:18,679 --> 00:54:19,679
[SPEAKER_00] a kuća u nizu,

1470
00:54:19,679 --> 00:54:21,099
[SPEAKER_00] pa propuh da mi vuče

1471
00:54:21,099 --> 00:54:23,760
[SPEAKER_00] od prednjih vrata

1472
00:54:23,760 --> 00:54:24,820
[SPEAKER_00] u dvorište,

1473
00:54:25,219 --> 00:54:26,539
[SPEAKER_00] prašinu dok metem

1474
00:54:26,539 --> 00:54:28,900
[SPEAKER_00] i dva šišmiša lete

1475
00:54:28,900 --> 00:54:31,340
[SPEAKER_00] i krilom

1476
00:54:31,340 --> 00:54:32,940
[SPEAKER_00] pukne me po glavi.

1477
00:54:32,940 --> 00:54:34,199
[SPEAKER_00] I ode tamo,

1478
00:54:34,199 --> 00:54:34,860
[SPEAKER_00] naježi se,

1479
00:54:34,860 --> 00:54:36,619
[SPEAKER_00] pa reko nije mu se radar pokvario,

1480
00:54:36,619 --> 00:54:37,480
[SPEAKER_00] kako me je pogodio.

1481
00:54:37,480 --> 00:54:41,139
[SPEAKER_00] Vraća se iz onog dvorišta,

1482
00:54:41,139 --> 00:54:42,599
[SPEAKER_00] opet me lupi po glavi.

1483
00:54:43,980 --> 00:54:45,119
[SPEAKER_00] Ja se naježi rako,

1484
00:54:45,119 --> 00:54:46,440
[SPEAKER_00] Bože, ovo nešto nije normalno.

1485
00:54:46,440 --> 00:54:48,219
[SPEAKER_00] Eto ih opet lete,

1486
00:54:48,219 --> 00:54:49,480
[SPEAKER_00] kona dva iz našibenika.

1487
00:54:49,480 --> 00:54:52,280
[SPEAKER_00] Ja kažem u ime Isusa,

1488
00:54:52,280 --> 00:54:53,059
[SPEAKER_00] na zarećenina,

1489
00:54:53,059 --> 00:54:54,420
[SPEAKER_00] zapovjedam ti zli duše,

1490
00:54:54,420 --> 00:54:55,260
[SPEAKER_00] odstupi od mene,

1491
00:54:55,260 --> 00:54:56,619
[SPEAKER_00] ja nisam tvoj nego Kristov,

1492
00:54:56,619 --> 00:54:58,619
[SPEAKER_00] u ime Oca i Sina i Duha Svetoga.

1493
00:54:58,619 --> 00:54:59,019
[SPEAKER_00] Amen.

1494
00:54:59,019 --> 00:55:02,360
[SPEAKER_00] Odoše,

1495
00:55:02,360 --> 00:55:03,340
[SPEAKER_00] raširiše se

1496
00:55:03,340 --> 00:55:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] i nisu se više vratili.

1497
00:55:05,000 --> 00:55:06,980
[SPEAKER_00] I nije ti sve jedno,

1498
00:55:06,980 --> 00:55:08,820
[SPEAKER_00] gađaju te točno.

1499
00:55:08,820 --> 00:55:13,739
[SPEAKER_00] I za toga meni počne riječići.

1500
00:55:13,980 --> 00:55:16,139
[SPEAKER_00] sarkom,

1501
00:55:16,139 --> 00:55:17,940
[SPEAKER_00] sarkom,

1502
00:55:17,940 --> 00:55:19,780
[SPEAKER_00] istim tempom konišišmiši.

1503
00:55:19,780 --> 00:55:20,760
[SPEAKER_00] Sarkom,

1504
00:55:20,760 --> 00:55:22,400
[SPEAKER_00] a baš mi jedna prijateljica obrva

1505
00:55:22,400 --> 00:55:24,320
[SPEAKER_00] od sarkoma pluća,

1506
00:55:24,320 --> 00:55:26,300
[SPEAKER_00] neizlječivi rak,

1507
00:55:26,300 --> 00:55:27,119
[SPEAKER_00] je li?

1508
00:55:27,119 --> 00:55:28,760
[SPEAKER_00] Najježiš se.

1509
00:55:28,760 --> 00:55:29,099
[SPEAKER_00] Ja kažem,

1510
00:55:29,099 --> 00:55:29,820
[SPEAKER_00] zli duše,

1511
00:55:29,820 --> 00:55:31,920
[SPEAKER_00] sarkom zapovjedam ti u ime Isusovo,

1512
00:55:31,920 --> 00:55:32,679
[SPEAKER_00] odstupi od mene,

1513
00:55:32,679 --> 00:55:34,159
[SPEAKER_00] ja nisam tvoj nego Kristov.

1514
00:55:34,159 --> 00:55:37,920
[SPEAKER_00] I prestane taj glas unutra koji,

1515
00:55:37,920 --> 00:55:38,940
[SPEAKER_00] nisi ga mogo istirati.

1516
00:55:38,940 --> 00:55:41,659
[SPEAKER_00] I to sam shvatio,

1517
00:55:41,659 --> 00:55:42,440
[SPEAKER_00] čekaj, čekaj.

1518
00:55:43,739 --> 00:55:45,460
[SPEAKER_00] Sotona koji je destruktivac,

1519
00:55:45,460 --> 00:55:47,159
[SPEAKER_00] koji ruši ono što je stvoreno,

1520
00:55:47,159 --> 00:55:50,320
[SPEAKER_00] on se kao otac laži prikriva

1521
00:55:50,320 --> 00:55:52,619
[SPEAKER_00] pod medicinska imena.

1522
00:55:52,619 --> 00:55:53,820
[SPEAKER_00] Pa onda tu ne očekuješ

1523
00:55:53,820 --> 00:55:54,940
[SPEAKER_00] da bi djavo mogao biti,

1524
00:55:54,940 --> 00:55:56,519
[SPEAKER_00] e onda od tada stanu, molim,

1525
00:55:56,519 --> 00:55:57,639
[SPEAKER_00] zli duše,

1526
00:55:57,639 --> 00:55:59,179
[SPEAKER_00] pa pročitam diagnozu.

1527
00:55:59,179 --> 00:56:00,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ja nisam tvoj nego Kristov,

1528
00:56:00,960 --> 00:56:01,960
[SPEAKER_00] gospodine,

1529
00:56:01,960 --> 00:56:03,079
[SPEAKER_00] ti se bori protiv njega,

1530
00:56:03,079 --> 00:56:04,719
[SPEAKER_00] ja nisam njegov nego tvoji.

1531
00:56:06,099 --> 00:56:08,360
[SPEAKER_00] Moji se liječe i ne izliječe,

1532
00:56:08,360 --> 00:56:10,139
[SPEAKER_00] a meni odlaze tako bolesti.

1533
00:56:10,139 --> 00:56:14,360
[SPEAKER_00] I onda se dogodi da me zove žena iz Mostara,

1534
00:56:14,360 --> 00:56:16,519
[SPEAKER_00] iz Mostarske bolnice,

1535
00:56:16,519 --> 00:56:16,900
[SPEAKER_00] kaže,

1536
00:56:16,900 --> 00:56:17,519
[SPEAKER_00] gospodine,

1537
00:56:17,519 --> 00:56:18,699
[SPEAKER_00] moli vas,

1538
00:56:18,699 --> 00:56:19,519
[SPEAKER_00] pomolite se,

1539
00:56:19,519 --> 00:56:20,440
[SPEAKER_00] kad god ste molili,

1540
00:56:20,440 --> 00:56:21,260
[SPEAKER_00] bilo mi je lakše,

1541
00:56:21,260 --> 00:56:22,699
[SPEAKER_00] a sad mi je velika potreba.

1542
00:56:22,699 --> 00:56:23,619
[SPEAKER_00] Pa što se dogodilo?

1543
00:56:23,619 --> 00:56:25,559
[SPEAKER_00] Pa evo,

1544
00:56:25,559 --> 00:56:26,619
[SPEAKER_00] došla sam na kontrolu,

1545
00:56:26,679 --> 00:56:28,639
[SPEAKER_00] sletijeli se doktori ovdje u rodilištu,

1546
00:56:28,639 --> 00:56:29,860
[SPEAKER_00] ja pitam,

1547
00:56:29,860 --> 00:56:31,320
[SPEAKER_00] nešto nije u redu s mojom bebicom,

1548
00:56:31,320 --> 00:56:31,579
[SPEAKER_00] kaže,

1549
00:56:31,579 --> 00:56:32,019
[SPEAKER_00] gospodin,

1550
00:56:32,019 --> 00:56:32,820
[SPEAKER_00] nažalost nije,

1551
00:56:32,820 --> 00:56:34,800
[SPEAKER_00] vaša bebica ima previše ruku i nogu.

1552
00:56:34,800 --> 00:56:36,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ja mislim,

1553
00:56:36,500 --> 00:56:37,420
[SPEAKER_00] Marko, čekaj,

1554
00:56:37,420 --> 00:56:38,119
[SPEAKER_00] to nije istina.

1555
00:56:38,119 --> 00:56:40,400
[SPEAKER_00] To nije istina.

1556
00:56:40,400 --> 00:56:41,659
[SPEAKER_00] Bog nije loš majstor

1557
00:56:41,659 --> 00:56:42,659
[SPEAKER_00] koji ne zna napraviti

1558
00:56:42,659 --> 00:56:44,300
[SPEAKER_00] normalnog čovjeka.

1559
00:56:44,300 --> 00:56:47,280
[SPEAKER_00] Nego to ne prijatelj boži i ljudski,

1560
00:56:47,280 --> 00:56:50,159
[SPEAKER_00] ruga se slici i prilici božioj,

1561
00:56:50,159 --> 00:56:51,500
[SPEAKER_00] pa pravi nakaz u nekakvu.

1562
00:56:51,500 --> 00:56:54,039
[SPEAKER_00] U ime Isusa nazarećanina moga,

1563
00:56:54,039 --> 00:56:55,039
[SPEAKER_00] Boga i gospodina,

1564
00:56:55,139 --> 00:56:58,019
[SPEAKER_00] odstupi taj zloduh sa svojom kreaturom,

1565
00:56:58,019 --> 00:57:01,679
[SPEAKER_00] a ti rodi onoga čovjeka

1566
00:57:01,679 --> 00:57:04,400
[SPEAKER_00] što ga je Bog Otac poželio stvoriti,

1567
00:57:04,400 --> 00:57:06,239
[SPEAKER_00] a tebe odredio da mu budeš majka

1568
00:57:06,239 --> 00:57:08,719
[SPEAKER_00] u ime Otca i Sina i Duha Svetoga.

1569
00:57:08,719 --> 00:57:09,139
[SPEAKER_00] Amen.

1570
00:57:09,139 --> 00:57:11,340
[SPEAKER_00] I sutradan me zove,

1571
00:57:11,340 --> 00:57:11,760
[SPEAKER_00] kaže,

1572
00:57:11,760 --> 00:57:12,880
[SPEAKER_00] Bogu dragom,

1573
00:57:12,880 --> 00:57:14,159
[SPEAKER_00] hvala i dobrom Isusu,

1574
00:57:14,159 --> 00:57:16,500
[SPEAKER_00] ja rodila najnormalniju djevojčicu.

1575
00:57:16,500 --> 00:57:19,099
[SPEAKER_00] I kad sam prije nekoliko godina

1576
00:57:19,099 --> 00:57:20,960
[SPEAKER_00] bio dolje u Mostarskoj jednoj školi,

1577
00:57:20,960 --> 00:57:22,400
[SPEAKER_00] izvodio onu predstavu

1578
00:57:22,400 --> 00:57:24,239
[SPEAKER_00] divlje konja za džake,

1579
00:57:25,139 --> 00:57:26,880
[SPEAKER_00] veli ravnateljevo tu neke gospodje

1580
00:57:26,880 --> 00:57:28,239
[SPEAKER_00] s djetetom htjela bi do vas.

1581
00:57:28,239 --> 00:57:29,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ona dođe i kaže,

1582
00:57:29,519 --> 00:57:31,679
[SPEAKER_00] evo moje Katarine za koju ste vi molili.

1583
00:57:31,679 --> 00:57:33,820
[SPEAKER_00] Reko, pa što su rekli doktori?

1584
00:57:35,900 --> 00:57:39,860
[SPEAKER_00] Pa tri doktora neovisno su gledali na ultrazvuk

1585
00:57:39,860 --> 00:57:41,619
[SPEAKER_00] i sve tri potvrdili isto.

1586
00:57:41,619 --> 00:57:43,539
[SPEAKER_00] Da bebica ima tri ruke

1587
00:57:43,539 --> 00:57:45,820
[SPEAKER_00] i da se ne može normalno roditi,

1588
00:57:45,820 --> 00:57:47,139
[SPEAKER_00] nego mora na carski rez.

1589
00:57:47,139 --> 00:57:49,039
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, nastala strka u rodilištu,

1590
00:57:49,039 --> 00:57:50,599
[SPEAKER_00] nisu me pripravili za carski,

1591
00:57:50,599 --> 00:57:53,639
[SPEAKER_00] ja dobila trudove i rodila najnormalnije dijete.

1592
00:57:54,380 --> 00:57:56,179
[SPEAKER_00] To dijete ide u školu.

1593
00:57:57,920 --> 00:58:01,300
[SPEAKER_00] Eto što ti je vjera

1594
00:58:01,300 --> 00:58:03,219
[SPEAKER_00] i boravak u tišini

1595
00:58:03,219 --> 00:58:05,840
[SPEAKER_00] i u mraku.

1596
00:58:05,840 --> 00:58:08,579
[SPEAKER_00] Uvijek s Bogom

1597
00:58:08,579 --> 00:58:10,579
[SPEAKER_00] kad ideš među ljude,

1598
00:58:10,579 --> 00:58:12,219
[SPEAKER_00] jer ako nemaš Boga u sebi,

1599
00:58:12,219 --> 00:58:13,599
[SPEAKER_00] nemaš čovjeku što dati?

1600
00:58:13,599 --> 00:58:15,820
[SPEAKER_00] Jer onda daješ ljubav i istinu,

1601
00:58:15,820 --> 00:58:17,480
[SPEAKER_00] a to je jedino što mi nemamo

1602
00:58:17,480 --> 00:58:18,360
[SPEAKER_00] u ovome svijetu.

1603
00:58:20,139 --> 00:58:22,420
[SPEAKER_00] A onda Sotonate ne može podnijeti.

1604
00:58:22,420 --> 00:58:25,699
[SPEAKER_00] Pa kad sam vodio ove svoje emisije,

1605
00:58:25,699 --> 00:58:29,059
[SPEAKER_00] ovih pet emisija na Radio Velikoj Gorici,

1606
00:58:29,059 --> 00:58:33,519
[SPEAKER_00] 238 nedjelja sam ja vodio te emisije

1607
00:58:33,519 --> 00:58:34,699
[SPEAKER_00] od početka rata,

1608
00:58:34,699 --> 00:58:38,139
[SPEAKER_00] 71. pa do 2000. godine poslje rata.

1609
00:58:38,139 --> 00:58:44,099
[SPEAKER_00] 238 nedjelja je bilo.

1610
00:58:44,099 --> 00:58:48,039
[SPEAKER_00] To da znate kakvih otpora je bilo,

1611
00:58:48,039 --> 00:58:49,139
[SPEAKER_00] samo da to ne bude.

1612
00:58:49,639 --> 00:58:52,239
[SPEAKER_00] Između ostalog stižu prijeteća pisma.

1613
00:58:52,239 --> 00:58:55,420
[SPEAKER_00] Svaki dan plava koverta,

1614
00:58:55,420 --> 00:58:56,519
[SPEAKER_00] jedno stiže doma,

1615
00:58:56,519 --> 00:58:57,659
[SPEAKER_00] a jedno na radio.

1616
00:58:57,659 --> 00:59:01,739
[SPEAKER_00] Nabit ćemo tebe i tvojih pet okota

1617
00:59:01,739 --> 00:59:02,900
[SPEAKER_00] na kolac,

1618
00:59:02,900 --> 00:59:05,360
[SPEAKER_00] jer zbog tebe je rat u Hrvatskoj.

1619
00:59:05,360 --> 00:59:06,519
[SPEAKER_00] I nema potpisa.

1620
00:59:06,519 --> 00:59:08,599
[SPEAKER_00] I sad možeš misliti,

1621
00:59:08,599 --> 00:59:10,239
[SPEAKER_00] pročitaš to, sledi ti se krv,

1622
00:59:10,239 --> 00:59:11,059
[SPEAKER_00] nije baš sve jedno.

1623
00:59:11,059 --> 00:59:12,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ratna situacija, ko zna?

1624
00:59:12,500 --> 00:59:15,659
[SPEAKER_00] Ko je protiv tebe?

1625
00:59:15,659 --> 00:59:16,739
[SPEAKER_00] Svaki dan.

1626
00:59:16,739 --> 00:59:19,079
[SPEAKER_00] I ja kažem, gospodine,

1627
00:59:19,139 --> 00:59:21,139
[SPEAKER_00] ja opraštam toj nesretnoj duši,

1628
00:59:21,139 --> 00:59:21,980
[SPEAKER_00] koja to radi,

1629
00:59:21,980 --> 00:59:26,119
[SPEAKER_00] ali autor toga pisma nije taj čovjek,

1630
00:59:26,119 --> 00:59:26,880
[SPEAKER_00] nego Sotona.

1631
00:59:26,880 --> 00:59:28,880
[SPEAKER_00] A ja nisam njegov,

1632
00:59:28,880 --> 00:59:29,599
[SPEAKER_00] nego tvoji.

1633
00:59:29,599 --> 00:59:31,340
[SPEAKER_00] Tebi predajem parnicu svoju,

1634
00:59:31,340 --> 00:59:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] ti se bori protiv moga neprijatelja,

1635
00:59:33,000 --> 00:59:35,599
[SPEAKER_00] i odnesem pismo u unutrašnjem džepu

1636
00:59:35,599 --> 00:59:36,920
[SPEAKER_00] na sljedeću svetu misu.

1637
00:59:37,800 --> 00:59:39,019
[SPEAKER_00] I tako kažem, gospodine,

1638
00:59:39,019 --> 00:59:39,639
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam tvoj,

1639
00:59:39,639 --> 00:59:40,139
[SPEAKER_00] a ne njegov,

1640
00:59:40,139 --> 00:59:41,920
[SPEAKER_00] ti se bori protiv ovog neprijatelja,

1641
00:59:41,920 --> 00:59:42,659
[SPEAKER_00] koji mi prijeti.

1642
00:59:42,659 --> 00:59:45,619
[SPEAKER_00] Nijedno jedino prijeteće pismo

1643
00:59:45,619 --> 00:59:46,480
[SPEAKER_00] nije više stiglo.

1644
00:59:46,480 --> 00:59:47,940
[SPEAKER_00] Nijedno jedino.

1645
00:59:47,940 --> 00:59:51,320
[SPEAKER_00] I kad sam došao na radi,

1646
00:59:51,320 --> 00:59:51,860
[SPEAKER_00] onda mi je,

1647
00:59:51,860 --> 00:59:53,659
[SPEAKER_00] ovoga ravnatelj radi,

1648
00:59:53,659 --> 00:59:53,980
[SPEAKER_00] rekao,

1649
00:59:53,980 --> 00:59:56,059
[SPEAKER_00] evo, tu neka budala ti piše prijeteća pisma,

1650
00:59:56,059 --> 00:59:57,420
[SPEAKER_00] ja to bacam u kožu za smeće,

1651
00:59:57,420 --> 00:59:57,579
[SPEAKER_00] rekao,

1652
00:59:57,639 --> 00:59:58,219
[SPEAKER_00] ne smiješ tako,

1653
00:59:58,219 --> 01:00:00,440
[SPEAKER_00] ako je počeo rat protiv mene,

1654
01:00:00,440 --> 01:00:02,539
[SPEAKER_00] ja moram u rat ući i pobjediti.

1655
01:00:02,539 --> 01:00:03,300
[SPEAKER_00] Kako?

1656
01:00:03,300 --> 01:00:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sotonu se pobjeđuje samo vjerom,

1657
01:00:05,000 --> 01:00:05,780
[SPEAKER_00] nikako drug čije.

1658
01:00:05,780 --> 01:00:07,199
[SPEAKER_00] Onda sam,

1659
01:00:07,199 --> 01:00:08,739
[SPEAKER_00] kaže, eto ti ga tamo u košu,

1660
01:00:08,739 --> 01:00:09,280
[SPEAKER_00] pa ga uzmi.

1661
01:00:09,280 --> 01:00:11,659
[SPEAKER_00] I to sam pismo odnio tamo.

1662
01:00:11,659 --> 01:00:13,539
[SPEAKER_00] Poslije sam sreo progonitelja crkve,

1663
01:00:13,539 --> 01:00:14,920
[SPEAKER_00] koji je doživio obraćenje,

1664
01:00:14,920 --> 01:00:17,280
[SPEAKER_00] i kad se je krstio,

1665
01:00:17,280 --> 01:00:19,300
[SPEAKER_00] prvi kolo za 91.

1666
01:00:19,300 --> 01:00:21,480
[SPEAKER_00] on je plakao ko malo dijete,

1667
01:00:21,480 --> 01:00:22,480
[SPEAKER_00] on se je tresao,

1668
01:00:22,480 --> 01:00:23,360
[SPEAKER_00] kodaj na struju.

1669
01:00:23,360 --> 01:00:27,159
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže, zar sam se ja morao 50 godina boriti,

1670
01:00:27,579 --> 01:00:28,900
